{
  "texts": [
    "AI text generators and detection systems will likely continue to play a cat-and-mouse game.",
    "This is somewhat similar to the generation of spam emails.",
    "Both sides will continue to train their system to defeat the other.",
    "At this point in time, the AI generators are ahead in the game, making it nearly impossible to automatically detect their use, particularly in shorter passages of text.",
    "Competitors to Undetectable.AI are likely to emerge in the near future."
  ]
}